platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 1. 控制火车。2. 建设线路！

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Can you conduct your way out of chaos?

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: In Train Conductor World, managing the European Railway takes talent, fast instincts, and… courage? As you create rails to send trains on the right path, you’re rewarded for being risky. How many close calls are you willing to have before stopping a few trains? Each colorful stage boasts its own unique challenges—like Bruges, which has you tracing bridges over a busy canal. Balancing the locomotive lunacy is amazingly fun, but even failure results in satisfying crashes.
